OL,3,CMan dies after being found with
OL,4,Csuspected stab wounds
OL,6,FA man has died after being found with
OL,7,Fsuspected stab wounds in Market Rasen.
OL,9,FPolice received a call at 5.07pm on
OL,10,FThursday, 12 March, reporting that a
OL,11,Fman in his thirties had been found in
OL,12,FUnion Street with suspected stab
OL,13,Fwounds. He later died of his injuries.
OL,15,FA 55-year-old man has been arrested in
OL,16,Fconnection with the incident.
OL,18,FLincolnshire Police have warned that
OL,19,Fresidents will see an increased police
OL,20,Fpresence in the town as
OL,21,Finvestigation's continues.
